---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-archiledger/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Archi-Ledger | Precision & Stability in Accounting"
  description="ARCHI-LEDGER provides structural-integrity accounting, audit, tax, and advisory services for high-growth enterprises, engineered with architectural rigor."
  active="home"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-archiledger"
>
<main class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-al-margin-mobile md:px-al-margin-desktop py-al-margin-desktop md:py-24">

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="mb-al-margin-desktop md:mb-24 border border-primary p-8 md:p-12 bg-surface-container relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-3xl relative z-10">
    <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 border border-primary bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed font-al-label-sm text-al-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
      Precision &amp; Stability
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-al-headline-xl text-al-headline-lg-mobile md:text-al-headline-xl mb-6 text-primary">Structural Integrity for Financial Success.</h1>
    <p class="font-al-body-lg text-al-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mb-8">
      ARCHI-LEDGER provides precision-engineered accounting and advisory services for high-growth enterprises. Our methodology is built on the rigorous principles of architectural planning applied to financial systems.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/contact" class="bg-primary text-on-primary font-al-label-md text-al-label-md px-8 py-3 border border-primary hard-shadow-hover transition-all uppercase tracking-widest active:translate-y-0.5">Schedule Consultation</a>
      <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/services" class="bg-transparent text-primary font-al-label-md text-al-label-md px-8 py-3 border-2 border-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-all uppercase tracking-widest">Our Services</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-1/3 opacity-10 hidden lg:block">
    <div class="w-full h-full border-l border-primary grid grid-cols-4 grid-rows-6">
      <div class="border-b border-r border-primary"></div>
      <div class="border-b border-r border-primary"></div>
      <div class="border-b border-r border-primary"></div>
      <div class="border-b border-primary"></div>
      <div class="border-b border-r border-primary"></div>
      <div class="border-b border-r border-primary bg-primary"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Stats / Trust -->
<section class="mb-al-margin-desktop md:mb-24 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 border border-primary divide-x divide-y md:divide-y-0 divide-primary">
  <div class="p-8 text-center">
    <div class="font-al-headline-lg text-al-headline-lg text-primary">20+</div>
    <div class="font-al-label-sm text-al-label-sm uppercase text-on-surface-variant mt-2">Years of Precision</div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-8 text-center">
    <div class="font-al-headline-lg text-al-headline-lg text-primary">500+</div>
    <div class="font-al-label-sm text-al-label-sm uppercase text-on-surface-variant mt-2">Institutional Clients</div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-8 text-center">
    <div class="font-al-headline-lg text-al-headline-lg text-primary">$4B+</div>
    <div class="font-al-label-sm text-al-label-sm uppercase text-on-surface-variant mt-2">Assets Under Management</div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-8 text-center">
    <div class="font-al-headline-lg text-al-headline-lg text-primary">4</div>
    <div class="font-al-label-sm text-al-label-sm uppercase text-on-surface-variant mt-2">Global Offices</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Services Bento Grid -->
<section class="mb-al-margin-desktop md:mb-24">
  <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-al-headline-lg text-al-headline-lg text-primary uppercase">Core Disciplines</h2>
    <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/services" class="font-al-label-md text-al-label-md text-primary uppercase tracking-widest border-b-2 border-primary pb-1 hidden md:inline-block">View All Services</a>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 border-t border-l border-primary">
    <div class="p-10 border-r border-b border-primary bg-white hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6 block">account_balance_wallet</span>
      <h3 class="font-al-headline-md text-al-headline-md text-primary mb-3">Tax Planning &amp; Compliance</h3>
      <p class="font-al-body-md text-al-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Strategic corporate tax structuring and international tax optimization.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-10 border-r border-b border-primary bg-white hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6 block">fact_check</span>
      <h3 class="font-al-headline-md text-al-headline-md text-primary mb-3">Audit &amp; Assurance</h3>
      <p class="font-al-body-md text-al-body-md text-on-surface-variant">SEC and public company audits, internal control reviews, SOX compliance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-10 border-r border-b border-primary bg-white hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6 block">insights</span>
      <h3 class="font-al-headline-md text-al-headline-md text-primary mb-3">Business Advisory</h3>
      <p class="font-al-body-md text-al-body-md text-on-surface-variant">M&amp;A due diligence, outsourced CFO, and succession planning.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-10 border-r border-b border-primary bg-white hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6 block">search_check</span>
      <h3 class="font-al-headline-md text-al-headline-md text-primary mb-3">Forensic Accounting</h3>
      <p class="font-al-body-md text-al-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Fraud investigation, litigation support, and asset tracing.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Latest Insights -->
<section class="mb-al-margin-desktop md:mb-24">
  <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-al-headline-lg text-al-headline-lg text-primary uppercase">Strategic Insights</h2>
    <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/blog" class="font-al-label-md text-al-label-md text-primary uppercase tracking-widest border-b-2 border-primary pb-1 hidden md:inline-block">View All Insights</a>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 border-t border-l border-primary">
    <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/blog/structural-impact-global-minimum-tax-multinational-entities" class="p-8 border-r border-b border-primary bg-white hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors block">
      <span class="font-al-label-sm text-al-label-sm text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest">Regulation</span>
      <h3 class="font-al-headline-md text-al-headline-md text-primary mt-3">The Structural Impact of Global Minimum Tax on Multi-National Entities</h3>
    </a>
    <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/blog/blockchain-ledger-architecture-beyond-hype-audit-accuracy" class="p-8 border-r border-b border-primary bg-white hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors block">
      <span class="font-al-label-sm text-al-label-sm text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest">Technology</span>
      <h3 class="font-al-headline-md text-al-headline-md text-primary mt-3">Blockchain Ledger Architecture: Moving Beyond the Hype to Audit Accuracy</h3>
    </a>
    <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/blog/economic-stability-volatile-markets-fixed-grid-asset-approach" class="p-8 border-r border-b border-primary bg-white hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors block">
      <span class="font-al-label-sm text-al-label-sm text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest">Strategy</span>
      <h3 class="font-al-headline-md text-al-headline-md text-primary mt-3">Economic Stability in Volatile Markets: A Fixed-Grid Asset Approach</h3>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="border-2 border-primary p-12 text-center bg-primary text-on-primary">
  <h3 class="font-al-headline-lg text-al-headline-lg mb-4">Ready to Build a Better Foundation?</h3>
  <p class="font-al-body-md text-al-body-md mb-8 opacity-80 max-w-xl mx-auto">Contact our lead partners today for a structural audit of your current accounting practices.</p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
    <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/contact" class="bg-white text-primary border border-white px-10 py-3 font-al-label-md text-al-label-md uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-primary-fixed-dim transition-all">Schedule Consultation</a>
    <a href="/templates/accounting-archiledger/about" class="bg-transparent text-white border border-white px-10 py-3 font-al-label-md text-al-label-md uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">About the Firm</a>
  </div>
</section>

</main>
</TemplateLayout>
